HOST YOUR NEXT CORPORATE EVENT
Many businesses host their meetings and special events at Colony West Golf Club because of our consistent and excellent customer service and amazing custom menus.
We offer a complete full service facility with rooms that can accommodate over 300 guests. We can even complete your meeting with a round of golf on either of our 18 hole Championship courses.
To learn more or get a personalized proposal please fill out the inquiry form below.
OUR EVENT SPACES
At Colony West Golf Club, we have five event spaces for you to choose from to make your special day perfect. Our newly renovated indoor and outdoor sites are perfect for any size group.
BANQUET ROOM
Whether you're hosting your wedding reception or a corporate event, our banquet room is the perfect blank canvas to transform into anything you can imagine.
ON THE COURSE
Hold your ceremony and capture unique photos of your special day on our stunning, 18-hole golf course.
